🌟 Contest Alert! 🌟
Celebrating fathers and father figures today. 🧡

For many of us women, our mothers are both our fathers and mothers. Let's also honor those incredible women who have taken on the role of father in our lives.

💝 Win exclusive gifts from Indo Era — because every mother who played both roles deserves to be celebrated in style.

How to Enter:
1️⃣ Comment below with a heart-touching line for your mother & mention her name.
2️⃣ Post a picture with your father figure (can be your mom, dad, or anyone who raised you) on your Instagram Story and tag @indo.era.
3️⃣ DM us the same photo.

It’s that simple!
Let’s share their stories, spread love, and honor every pillar of strength in our lives. 💪✨

🎁 Lucky winners will be announced soon!
